OL,3,CSwansea teenager charged with murder
OL,4,Cas victim of fatal bike crash named
OL,6,FA teenager has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following a fatal crash in
OL,8,FSwansea.
OL,10,FTyler Ford, 18, from Morriston has
OL,11,Fbeen charged with the murder of Ceiran
OL,12,FEvans, also 18, from Gorseinon.
OL,14,FFord has also been charged with
OL,15,Fattempted murder of a second victim.
OL,17,FHe is remanded in custody to appear at
OL,18,FSwansea Magistrates' Court on Monday,
OL,19,F13 July, South Wales Police have
OL,20,Fconfirmed.
