OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784047674
OL,3,CSwansea teenager charged with murder
OL,4,Cas victim of fatal bike crash named
OL,6,FIt comes after police were called to
OL,7,FPen Cae Crwn Road, Gorseinon in
OL,8,FSwansea, at around 1pm on Thursday 9
OL,9,FJuly following a report of a collision
OL,10,Finvolving a car and an off-road bike.
OL,12,FA 19-year-old man remains in hospital.
OL,14,FPolice said that although formal
OL,15,Fidentification has not yet taken
OL,16,Fplace, the family of Ceiran Evans is
OL,17,Fbeing supported by specially trained
OL,18,Fofficers.
OL,20,FFour other men arrested as part of the
OL,21,Finvestigation are on police bail.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
