OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784047674
OL,3,CSwansea teenager charged with murder
OL,4,Cas victim of fatal bike crash named
OL,6,FThey are an 18-year-old man from
OL,7,FGorseinon arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder and Section 18 grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm with intent, a 33-year-old man
OL,10,Ffrom Gorseinon arrested on suspicion
OL,11,Fof murder, a 38-year-old man from
OL,12,FGowerton and a 38-year-old man from
OL,13,FMount Pleasant arrested on suspicion
OL,14,Fof assisting an offender.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Danielle
OL,17,FThorne of South Wales Police confirmed
OL,18,Fthat enquiries are continuing "at
OL,19,Fpace" and asked for anyone with
OL,20,Finformation to come forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
