OL,3,CSwansea teenager charged with murder
OL,4,Cas victim of fatal bike crash named
OL,6,F"I would once again like to thank the
OL,7,Fpeople of Gorseinon who have supported
OL,8,Fofficers both at the scene and come
OL,9,Fforward with information. It is very
OL,10,Fmuch appreciated," she said.
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Thorne added: "We are
OL,13,Faware of social media footage
OL,14,Fcirculating from this incident, and we
OL,15,Fonce again ask that this is not shared
OL,16,Ffor obvious reasons."
